		<title>Blood test shows promise for detecting testicular cancer when standard markers miss</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/blood-test-shows-promise-for-detecting-testicular-cancer-when-standard-markers-miss/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[gilliganjack]]--></dc:creator>
